ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#99: FILE: arch/ia64/kernel/perfmon.c:2288:
+	if ((ret = remap_vmalloc_range(vma, smpl_buf, 0))) {

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

